# =====================================================
# 🚀 Production Deployment Checklist
# =====================================================

# Before deploying:
# ☐ All REQUIRED variables are set (marked above)
# ☐ JWT_SECRET is changed (not default)
# ☐ MONGODB_URI points to production database
# ☐ EMAIL_USER and EMAIL_PASSWORD are correct
# ☐ FRONTEND_URL matches your deployment domain
# ☐ NODE_ENV is set to "production"
# ☐ All credentials are secure (no hardcoding)
